{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|peDismissal', 'text' : 'He who rose from the dead,'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Key0101|mode', 'text' : 'Mode pl. 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Key0101|text', 'text' : 'Come receive the light, from the never-setting light; and glorify Christ who has risen from the dead.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Key0102|mode', 'text' : 'Mode pl. 2.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Key0102|text', 'text' : 'Angels in the heavens extol Your Resurrection, O Christ our Savior. Count us worthy who are here on earth to glorify You with a pure heart.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|ChristIsRisen|mode', 'text' : 'Mode pl. 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|ChristIsRisen|text', 'text' : 'Christ is risen from the dead, by death trampling down upon death, and to those in the tombs He has granted life.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|ChristIsRisen1a|text', 'text' : 'Christ is risen from the dead, by death trampling down upon death, and to those in the tombs...'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|ChristIsRisen1b|text', 'text' : '...He has granted life.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|ChristIsRisen2a|text', 'text' : 'Christ is risen from the dead, by death trampling down upon death...'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|ChristIsRisen2b|text', 'text' : '...and to those in the tombs He has granted life.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|ChristIsRisenShort|text', 'text' : 'Christ is risen from the dead, by death trampling down upon death, and to those in the tombs He has granted life.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|PaschaVerse1|text', 'text' : 'Let God arise, and let His enemies be scattered, and let those who hate Him flee from before His face.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|PaschaVerse2|text', 'text' : 'As smoke vanishes, so let them vanish, as wax melts before the fire.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|PaschaVerse3|text', 'text' : 'So shall the sinners perish from the face of God. And let the righteous be glad.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|PaschaVerse4|text', 'text' : 'This is the day the Lord made; let us greatly rejoice and be glad therein.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Canon|Poet', 'text' : 'By John of Damascus.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Canon|text', 'text' : 'Canon of Pascha'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|CanonT|Acrostic', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode1H|ode', 'text' : 'Ode i.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode1H|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode1H|melody', 'text' : 'Heirmos.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode1H|text', 'text' : 'Resurrection Day! O peoples, let us brilliantly shine! * Pascha, the Lord's Pascha! * For Christ our God has out of death * passed us over into life, * and likewise from earth * to heaven, as we now sing * unto Him a triumphal hymn.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|C1|title', 'text' : 'Canon of Pascha.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|C1|verse', 'text' : 'Glory to Your holy Resurrection, O Lord.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode11|ode', 'text' : 'Ode i.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode11|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode11|melody', 'text' : 'Resurrection Day.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode11|text', 'text' : 'Let us purify our senses and then we shall see * by the unapproachable light of the Resurrection * Christ shining vividly, and we shall distinctly hear Him saying, Rejoice, to us * as we sing the triumphal hymn.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode12|ode', 'text' : 'Ode i.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode12|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode12|melody', 'text' : 'Resurrection Day.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode12|text', 'text' : 'Let the heavens, as is fitting, now be jubilant; * let the earth be exultant. * Let the entire cosmos, visible and invisible now celebrate the feast.* For Christ, our eternal joy, * has indeed from the dead been raised.'}
