{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode3H|ode', 'text' : 'Ode iii.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode3H|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode3H|melody', 'text' : 'Heirmos.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode3H|text', 'text' : 'Come and let us drink a new drink, * not one marvelously issuing from a barren rock, * but one that Christ from the tomb * pours out, incorruption's very source. * For we are established in Him.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode31|ode', 'text' : 'Ode iii.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode31|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode31|melody', 'text' : 'Come and let us drink.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode31|text', 'text' : 'Now everything, heaven and the earth * and the nethermost regions, have all been filled with light. * Let the entire creation, therefore, celebrate the rising of Christ. * For it is established in Him.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode32|ode', 'text' : 'Ode iii.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode32|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode32|melody', 'text' : 'Come and let us drink.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode32|text', 'text' : 'Buried with You yesterday, O Christ, * with You now resurrected, I also rise today. * Yesterday I was with You crucified. O Savior, with Yourself glorify me in Your rule.'}
