{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode5H|ode', 'text' : 'Ode v.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode5H|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode5H|melody', 'text' : 'Heirmos.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode5H|text', 'text' : 'Arising at dawn very early, * instead of ointment, a hymn let us offer unto the Master, * and then we shall clearly see* Christ, the Sun of Righteousness, * causing true life to arise for all.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode51|ode', 'text' : 'Ode v.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode51|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode51|melody', 'text' : 'Arising at dawn.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode51|text', 'text' : 'Beholding Your measureless compassion, the souls below that were held by the shackles and bonds of Hades pressing forward hastened to the light with feet exultant, O Christ, applauding the Pascha that never ends.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode52|ode', 'text' : 'Ode v.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode52|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 1.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode52|melody', 'text' : 'Arising at dawn.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode52|text', 'text' : 'With candles and lamps let us go out to be with Christ who emerged from the sepulcher like the Bridegroom; and with festive ranks of Angels let us also celebrate God's holy Pascha that saves us all.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d00P_en_US_dedes|pePA|Ode5T1|ode', 'text' : 'Ode v.'}
